{"tid":575544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE免考試費個開支大約係1.8億？邊個天才計出黎","createTime":"2018-02-28T09:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:19:45.000Z","uid":58174,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8d9e2d3846c461f206ea10c532e7c22d591f4b","tid":575544,"uid":58174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"一個全日制考生總共大約要比3000蚊左右，我當有6萬個考生已經1.8億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n  仲未計一大班裸考嘅成年人點只1.8億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76df039700468d38fbf4cbc3561738a88aaf858","tid":575544,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"現時2018年中學文憑試考試費用，語文科收費619元；其他科目為414元；自修生的報名費為475元。以一名報考6科，即兩個語文及四個非語文科目的學校考生計算，考試費為港幣 2,894 元。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士表示，今次是港府首次為全港考生代繳公開考試費用，不限年齡的自修生及學生考生均可受惠。被問到擔不擔心會有大量市民報考，消息稱政府歡迎市民進修，估計會多了一部分人應考，透露已「預鬆了」將金額，若最終比預算多，會再提交撥款申請。"},{"pid":"f1c7fed1060b3e7a9bf594b03b0dd3a2089cd8f4","tid":575544,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"冇成本點解唔做？"},{"pid":"cec07d7d1df4d6a0144f95f22e3af667027e9580","tid":575544,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"佢地比錢益蝗就乜都肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0472527b6031066f3a59755e6135161deb4398f3","tid":575544,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3a7a3476d5aa642e77ed9abd5923850b96eb1ed","tid":575544,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b8d9e2d3846c461f206ea10c532e7c22d591f4b","tid":575544,"uid":58174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"一個全日制考生總共大約要比3000蚊左右，我當有6萬個考生已經1.8億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n  仲未計一大班裸考嘅成年人點只1.8億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi